13:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"We partner with a third party to either display advertising on our website or to manage our advertising on other sites. Our third-party partner may use technologies such as cookies to gather information about your activities on this website and other sites in order to provide you advertising based upon your browsing activities and interests. If you wish to not have this information used for the purpose of serving you interest-based ads, you may opt-out by clicking here http://preferences-mgr.truste.com/ Please note this does not opt you out of being served ads. You will continue to receive generic ads."}]
14:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"You may access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information by contacting us at privacy@kflegacyresources.com. We will respond to your request within a reasonable timeframe. You can also contact your local Data Protection Authority."}]
15:["$","h4",null,{"className":"mb-3","children":"How do we safeguard your personal information?"}]
16:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"We use a range of security measures to protect your personal information. Please be aware, however, that KFLR cannot guarantee that third parties will safeguard your personal information in a similar manner. If you have any questions about the security of your personal information, you can contact us at privacy@kflegacyresources.com"}]
17:["$","h4",null,{"className":"mb-3","children":"How will we update this Policy?"}]
18:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"We may amend this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we materially change our Privacy Policy, we will take steps to inform you of the change through email, SMS, notices on our websites or other means. The \"Effective Date\" at the top of this Privacy Policy shows when it was last updated."}]
